<br />
If the weight problem is not worked out I hope I can get some nice strength items.  That way I could carry more arrows.   So far everything for my class seems to be geared for quickness and dexterity.  If those are the main stream items available for the scout class it would be better for the base class to be a Britain.  The reason being they have more hit points more strength and if the majority of the items the scouts gets are geared toward dexterity and quickness then the items will help your character more over all.  I get the feeling that the development team is being very careful with the scout class.  It is important for the scout class not to be too powerful.  
<br />
Maybe if we have to keep getting arrows the development team could give us some kind of running bonus?  Maybe make the arrows lighter?  Give scouts more strength?  Maybe the scouts could hire a NPC to follow them around carrying their arrows.
<br />
For now I will have to deal with not getting invited into groups or to continue getting kicked out of groups because I am too high maintenance for certain types of players.  It has only happened two times that I am aware of so far.  It really isn&#8217;t unplayable it usually only takes thirty minutes to re-supply.  
